query:
-- Get provider IDs
SET @openai_id = (SELECT id FROM model_providers WHERE name = 'openai');
SET @claude_id = (SELECT id FROM model_providers WHERE name = 'claude');

-- Insert OpenAI models
INSERT INTO models (providerId, modelName, displayName, description, maxTokens, costPer1kInput, costPer1kOutput, isActive, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@openai_id, 'gpt-4', 'GPT-4', 'Most capable GPT-4 model, great for complex tasks', 8192, '0.03', '0.06', TRUE, NOW()),
(@openai_id, 'gpt-4-turbo', 'GPT-4 Turbo', 'Faster and cheaper GPT-4 variant with 128k context', 128000, '0.01', '0.03', TRUE, NOW()),
(@openai_id, 'gpt-3.5-turbo', 'GPT-3.5 Turbo', 'Fast and cost-effective model for simple tasks', 4096, '0.0015', '0.002', TRUE, NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE displayName = VALUES(displayName), description = VALUES(description);

-- Insert Claude models
INSERT INTO models (providerId, modelName, displayName, description, maxTokens, costPer1kInput, costPer1kOutput, isActive, createdAt)
VALUES 
(@claude_id, 'claude-3-opus-20240229', 'Claude 3 Opus', 'Most powerful Claude model for complex analysis', 4096, '0.015', '0.075', TRUE, NOW()),
(@claude_id, 'claude-3-sonnet-20240229', 'Claude 3 Sonnet', 'Balanced performance and cost', 4096, '0.003', '0.015', TRUE, NOW()),
(@claude_id, 'claude-3-haiku-20240307', 'Claude 3 Haiku', 'Fastest and most compact Claude model', 4096, '0.00025', '0.00125', TRUE, NOW())
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE displayName = VALUES(displayName), description = VALUES(description);
